definition: a saw/to cut with a saw
tree/wood/coffin/wooden/simple/numb/one of the eight categories of ancient musical instruments 八音[ba1 yin1]

sentences.english: The Prussians are drilling in the meadow behind the sawmill.
sentences.chinese: 魯士士兵鋸木廠草操練。

sentences.english: They drift the logs down the river to the sawmills.
sentences.chinese: 他們使那些圓木漂下河流到鋸木廠。

sentences.english: It is necessary to exterminate the post at the sawmill.
sentences.chinese: 必須端掉鋸木廠邊的哨所。

sentences.english: The timber was snaked to sawmills.
sentences.chinese: 這些木材被拖到鋸木廠。

sentences.english: Prior to 1957, the company focused primarily on lumber mills and sawmills.
sentences.chinese: 1957年之前，該公司主要集中於板材廠和鋸木廠。

sentences.english: The logs were drifted down the stream to the saw-mills.
sentences.chinese: 原木順流而下漂向鋸木廠。

sentences.english: When I had asked him about the sawmill, he wasn't nearly as interested in that subject.
sentences.chinese: 當我向他詢問鋸木廠，他不近的興趣這一問題。

sentences.english: They are employed in sawmills and planing mills.
sentences.chinese: 他們受僱於鋸木廠及刨工廠。

sentences.english: The villagers set up a saw-mill at the foot of the mountain.
sentences.chinese: 村民們在山腳下建造了一個鋸木廠。

sentences.english: I loved spending the night with Papaw at the sawmill.
sentences.chinese: 我很喜歡晚上和外公一起待在鋸木廠裏。

sentences.english: Reductions in credit lines hurt sawmills'ability to buy timber still available.
sentences.chinese: 銀行貸款的減少傷害了鋸木廠購買僅存木材的能力。

sentences.english: The results from the two sawmills indicate that the sawmill chips can be improved.
sentences.chinese: 得出的結果表明，兩個鋸木廠的鋸木廠芯片可以改進。

sentences.english: The results from the two sawmills indicate that the sawmill chips can be improved.
sentences.chinese: 得出的結果表明，兩個鋸木廠的鋸木廠芯片可以改進。

sentences.english: Find portable sawmills, and recording machines, grinding machines.
sentences.chinese: 查找便攜式鋸木廠，集材機，研磨機。

sentences.english: The trees are harvested by lumberjacks and sent to a sawmill.
sentences.chinese: 這些樹是收穫的伐木工和發送到鋸木廠。
